      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_assignment_in_onedrive" data-step-uuid="7583f67f-cdd1-4210-b97a-60e486aa3a86">
    <h2 id="open_assignment_in_onedrive" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Document Editor</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/922/646/original/97f4d3d5-d230-483c-8d12-4a00cad7c9b8.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/922/646/medium/97f4d3d5-d230-483c-8d12-4a00cad7c9b8.png" srcset="" alt="Open Document Editor" height="551" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_1B331680-22EE-0135-112E-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To complete the assignment from the assignments page, click the Edit Document drop-down menu and select <strong>Edit</strong> [1].</p>
<p>To open the assignment using the corresponding app, select <strong>Open in Desktop App</strong> [2]. </p>
<p>To open the assignment in a separate window, click the <strong>Open </strong>button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="edit_in_word" data-step-uuid="60772aae-96d9-4bd5-8040-0376369b5d81">
    <h2 id="edit_in_word" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Edit Assignment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/922/648/original/5e7fec3c-0db6-4096-b89f-27da6ab1cbd7.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
